## Implied Capital Charge, not accounting for exposure

$$
\mathrm{ICC}(r) = \frac{
    \mathrm{State WPLR}
}{
    \mathrm{WPLR}(r)
} 
$$

$$
\mathrm{WPLR}(r) = \frac{
\sum_p \mathrm{AAL}(p,r)
}{
    \sum_p \frac{
        1
    }{
